headline: Texas Instruments board declares fourth quarter 2025 quarterly dividend
summary: The board of directors of Texas Instruments Incorporated (Nasdaq: TXN) today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.42 per share of common stock, payable Nov. 12, 2025, to stockholders of record on Oct. 31, 2025.

headline: TI names President and CEO Haviv Ilan as chairman of the board
summary: Texas Instruments Incorporated (TI) (Nasdaq: TXN) today announced that its board of directors has elected President and Chief Executive Officer Haviv Ilan to take on the additional role as chairman, beginning January 2026. Ilan succeeds Rich Templeton, who will retire at the end of 2025 after a 45-year career with the company.
